John Roos

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search

For the English baron spelled "John Roos" or "John de Roos", see John de Ros.


John Roos








28th United States Ambassador to Japan


In office
August 20, 2009 – August 12, 2013


President
Barack Obama


Preceded by
Tom Schieffer


Succeeded by
