SalesU 2.0 Suite will be Featured at TrailheaDX with AI-driven Solutions in 30+ Languages and Productivity Enhancements EdCast announces the launch of SalesU 2.0, the most robust end-to-end sales enablement suite available for mid-to-large enterprises. The SalesU Suite addresses sales team productivity across three dimensions, which correspond to the three core solutions in the SalesU suite.

















