Insider Activity


Individual




John Victor Roos



Mr. John V. Roos is Chief Executive Officer at The Ross Group, Inc. (Indiana). He is on the Board of Directors at Sony Corp. and salesforce.com, inc. Mr. Roos was previously employed as Chief Executive Officer & Senior Partner by Wilson Sonsini Goodrich & Rosati PC. He received his undergraduate degree from Stanford University and a graduate degree from Stanford Law School.



